About
We are a small, elegant cocktail jazz lounge located in the Tenderloin. We have a full bar, but take special pride in our vast and growing collection of the world's best rums. Our Jazz days are Friday and Saturday.
Rum-focused bar with craft cocktails in the Tenderloin. Our happy hour is 4:00 PM to 7:00 PM
General Manager
zhuravskaya olga
categories
Cocktail Bar
STORY
Rum&Sugar
We are a beautiful hidden pearl, and a craft cocktail jazz lounge in the Tenderloin with a full bar and a particular focus on rum and Jazz music. We play Jazz every Thursday, Friday. We have a DJ on Saturday, we taste rums, and we like to have a good time all week long.
